text: Atlacomulco Cathedral is a large Modern Catholic cathedral in Mexico and is found in the city of Atlacomulco in Mexico (state). The new cathedral is next to where the old cathedral was. ==Bishops== * Juan Pedro Juárez Meléndez == Other websites == Category:Roman Catholic cathedrals in Mexico Category:Buildings and structures in Mexico (state) Category:Atlacomulco
